item.title: Billy Stokes' Photographic Stories
item.description:
Billy Stokes' Photographic Stories

Adam This seems to be a name that I am getting familiar with while on the streets meeting new & interesting people. This time, Adam was a musician. Rather than being a life-defending, witch-watcher, who's name I was not certain was actually Adam, this Adam was a Geography-teaching, ciggy-smoking, unemployed, uneducated tiger.
